  ('generalpolice-3218f787-moex-00097', 'generalpolice-3218f787', 'generalpolice-3218f787-moex-114-90de4de6', 'sub-generalpolice-3218f787-06', NULL, 'essay', '某項政府調查報告書中指出，「本調查之抽樣方法係採用分層隨機抽樣，
